<item>
 <title>Experimentação</title>
 <link>http://redelabs.org/blog/experimentacao</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/bruces&quot;&gt;Bruce Sterling&lt;/a&gt;, no &lt;a href=&quot;http://video.reboot.dk/video/486788/bruce-sterling-reboot-11&quot;&gt;encerramento do Reboot 11&lt;/a&gt; (em 2009):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&quot;Ok, você está mesmo &#039;experimentando&#039;? Como você sabe se está mesmo experimentando? Você está trabalhando metodicamente e está publicando os resultados! Não é um experimento se você não publicar em um formato verificável e refutável, ok?&quot; 
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-3 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/sterling&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;sterling&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/experimentacao&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;experimentação&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-2 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Categoria:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wordpress-category/pessoas&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;pessoas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <pubDate>Tue, 05 Apr 2011 15:47:08 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>efeefe</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">52 at http://redelabs.org</guid>
